Kenyan Government Plans to ‘Simplify’ Requirements for Tax in Next Budget

-- B y   S a r a h   M c G r e g o r
-- 
2011-03-21T08:00:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/kenyan-government-plans-to-simplify-requirements-for-tax-in-next-budget.html
Kenya plans to “simplify” its
requirements for tax payments in the 2011-12 budget to improve
“efficiency” and boost revenue, Kenyan Finance Minister  Uhuru
Kenyatta  said.  The measures may include removing Value-Added Tax
exemptions, he told reporters today in Nairobi, the capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah McGregor in Nairobi at 
 smcgregor5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  